About This Company
Times of Arabia Restaurant combines a genuine premium Lebanese culinary experience with the fine taste of the Levant region and the magical atmosphere of five millennia of Arab legacy.
The first Times of Arabia Restaurant, at the Souk Madinat Jumeirah has become a reputed attraction at the world-famous tourist destination. Times of Arabia Restaurant has again opened in Dubai Mall delighting its customers with the mouth-watering Mezzas, Grills, and an array of classic dishes from all over the Middle East. The richly adorned interior surrounded by luxurious color, handcrafted furniture, and one of a kind artworks.
Its customers will enjoy the Dance Shows several times a day which are guaranteed to keep guests of all ages and places thoroughly entertained throughout their meal.
